reviewText: Aaron Yan is a phenomenal actor.  He made both characters stand out independently of one another making it believable that they were not the same person.  This is a great story and the cast of actors do an amazing job of weaving you into the drama.
Even though I own it,I still watch it on Netflix. Watched over and over,both film and tv. great ending.
I love it so much.  wow
It was such a great drama that I purchased it! Defiantly a must watch and must buy. Aaron Yan is a very talented actor, and singer! He is also quite a looker too! Wonderful drama, five stars
Show is good, the english... well off is one word.  You get the general jist put it that way.  If you want decent english, watch it on dramafever.com

I thoroughly enjoyed watching this Taiwanese drama. I would love for someone in my family to purchase this item for my birthday. This will really help me with polishing up my Mandarin Chinese. However,I would like to have a set which will have no problems.
The inside of the case was plain and a piece was broken. The English subs are off as well. Should not cost $75.00. I feel like I was robbed Smh...
